{
  "stem": "26486.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So anyway, I said, my friends, I want my hair to grow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I used my-- I'd tell them-- use that soap like shampoo.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they'd massage my-- my head with the soap.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Yeah, we-- we had some laughters too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't always cry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at night, we'd be punished because when we went to bed, we'd all-- I think it was 8:00, no more noise or anything.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't talk, no noise.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then we would sing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We'd sing one religious song or something to put us to sleep.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they'd come in with the dogs and they'd-- oh, they were so cruel with us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They'd make us keep quiet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't even have that-- the liberty to sing, say goodnight, or even say a prayer, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, you spoke-- you spoke a number of languages.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I first got there?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not in-- yeah, in Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I-- first jobs I had were all hard labor, not good jobs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I only got the good job at Siemens later on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was sick after that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had the hard labor and then I fell sick with typhus, then I had endemic typhus.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had blood poison, my two legs, I told you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had worms coming out of my-- my legs, out of the holes in my legs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hm?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
